headline: Robinhood Chief Legal Officer Gallagher is Frontrunner To Replace SEC Chair Gensler
summary: Former SEC commissioner Dan Gallagher, 45, has emerged as a top candidate to lead the Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC) following Donald Trump’s presidential election win.
